              <Attribute Type="Description">For discussion of the 3-kb deletion in the PLOD1 gene that was found in compound heterozygous state in a patient with kyphoscoliotic Ehlers-Danlos syndrome (EDSKSCL1; 225400) by Pousi et al. (1998), see 153454.0005.</Attribute>
